39
00:02:35,100 --> 00:02:37,700
Quote, "When I love God,

40
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:40,100
I love the beauty of bodies,

41
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:42,700
the rhythm of movements,

42
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:44,700
the shining of eyes,

43
00:02:44,700 --> 00:02:46,500
the embraces,

44
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:47,700
the feelings,

45
00:02:47,700 --> 00:02:49,100
the sense,

46
00:02:49,100 --> 00:02:53,900
the sense of all these protein creation.

47
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:56,100
When I love you, my God,

48
00:02:56,100 --> 00:02:58,700
I want to embrace it all,

49
00:02:58,700 --> 00:03:01,500
for I love you with all my senses

50
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:04,500
in the creations of your love.

51
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:08,100
In all the things that encounter me,

52
00:03:08,100 --> 00:03:11,700
