53
00:03:11,700 --> 00:03:13,900
The experience of God

54
00:03:13,900 --> 00:03:17,300
deepens the experiences of life.

55
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:19,100
It does not reduce them,

56
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:20,300
for they are ways

57
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:24,500
the unconditional yes to life.

58
00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:26,300
The more I love God,

59
00:03:26,300 --> 00:03:29,100
the more gladly I exist.

60
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:32,700
The more immediately and wholly I exist,

61
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:35,700
the more I sense the living God,

62
00:03:35,700 --> 00:03:38,500
the inexhaustible source of life

63
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:40,900
and eternal livingness."

64
00:03:40,900 --> 00:03:42,900
End quote.

65
00:03:42,900 --> 00:03:45,700
Such a great passion for life

66
00:03:45,700 --> 00:03:47,700
is why we are so thankful

67
00:03:47,700 --> 00:03:50,300
to have him in our midst tonight

68
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:52,500
