70
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:55,300
a culture of life

71
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:58,500
in the dangers of our time.

72
00:03:58,500 --> 00:03:59,900
So please join me

73
00:03:59,900 --> 00:04:01,700
