81
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:28,900
the famous professor,

82
00:04:28,900 --> 00:04:31,900
Professor Daniel Lee.

83
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:34,900
Ladies and gentlemen,

84
00:04:34,900 --> 00:04:37,900
I grapple with what have been

85
00:04:37,900 --> 00:04:41,900
