86
00:04:41,900 --> 00:04:43,900
for some time,

87
00:04:43,900 --> 00:04:45,900
a culture of life

88
00:04:45,900 --> 00:04:50,900
stronger than the terror of death,

89
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:53,900
a love for life

90
00:04:53,900 --> 00:04:55,900
that overcomes

91
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:58,900
the destructive forces

92
00:04:58,900 --> 00:05:01,900
in our world today

93
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:03,900
and a confidence

94
00:05:03,900 --> 00:05:05,900
in the future

95
00:05:05,900 --> 00:05:08,900
that overcomes anxiety

96
00:05:08,900 --> 00:05:11,900
and fatalism.

97
00:05:11,900 --> 00:05:14,900
These issues are for me

98
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:17,900
most urgent

