116
00:06:15,900 --> 00:06:17,900
And in part two,

117
00:06:17,900 --> 00:06:20,900
I will offer some answers

118
00:06:20,900 --> 00:06:23,900
by considering dimensions

119
00:06:23,900 --> 00:06:26,900
of the world

120
00:06:26,900 --> 00:06:30,900
capable of supporting life

